# Sūra LXIX.: Ḥāqqa, or the Sure Reality.

### Section 2

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_038.gif)

38. Fal<u>a</u> oqsimu bim<u>a</u> tub<u>s</u>iroon**a**

38\. So I do  
Call to witness  
What ye see

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_039.gif)

39. Wam<u>a</u> l<u>a</u> tub<u>s</u>iroon**a**

39\. And what ye see not,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_040.gif)

40. Innahu laqawlu rasoolin kareem**in**

40\. That this is  
Verily the word  
Of an honoured apostle;

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_041.gif)

41. Wam<u>a</u> huwa biqawli sh<u>a</u>AAirin qaleelan m<u>a</u>
tu/minoon**a**

41\. It is not the word  
Of a poet:  
Little it is  
Ye believe!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_042.gif)

42. Wal<u>a</u> biqawli k<u>a</u>hinin qaleelan m<u>a</u>
ta<u>th</u>akkaroon**a**

42\. Nor is it the word  
Of a soothsayer:  
Little admonition it is  
Ye receive.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_043.gif)

43. Tanzeelun min rabbi alAA<u>a</u>lameen**a**

43\. (This is) a Message  
Sent down from the Lord  
Of the Worlds.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_044.gif)

44. Walaw taqawwala AAalayn<u>a</u> baAA<u>d</u>a al-aq<u>a</u>weel**i**

44\. And if the apostle  
Were to invent  
Any sayings in Our name,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_045.gif)

45. Laakha<u>th</u>n<u>a</u> minhu bi**a**lyameen**i**

45\. We should certainly seize him  
By his right hand,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_046.gif)

46. Thumma laqa<u>t</u>aAAn<u>a</u> minhu alwateen**a**

46\. And We should certainly  
Then cut off the artery  
Of his heart:

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_047.gif)

47. Fam<u>a</u> minkum min a<u>h</u>adin AAanhu <u>ha</u>jizeen**a**

47\. Nor could any of you  
Withhold him  
(From Our wrath).

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_048.gif)

48. Wa-innahu lata<u>th</u>kiratun lilmuttaqeen**a**

48\. But verily this  
Is a Message for  
The God-fearing.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_049.gif)

49. Wa-inn<u>a</u> lanaAAlamu anna minkum muka<u>thth</u>ibeen**a**

49\. And We certainly know  
That there are amongst you  
Those that reject (it).

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_050.gif)

50. Wa-innahu la<u>h</u>asratun AAal<u>a</u> alk<u>a</u>fireen**a**

50\. But truly (Revelation)  
Is a cause of sorrow  
For the Unbelievers.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_051.gif)

51. Wa-innahu la<u>h</u>aqqu alyaqeen**i**

51\. But verily it is Truth  
Of assured certainty.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/069/069_052.gif)

52. Fasabbi<u>h</u> bi**i**smi rabbika alAAa*<u>th</u>*eem**i**

52\. So glorify the name  
Of thy Lord Most High.

